"out=\"object.partner_id.name or '''John Doe'''\"/>,</p>\n"
"                <p style=\"margin:0px 0 16px 0;box-sizing:border-box;"
"\">We're looking forward to capturing\n"
"                    your photographs\n"
"                    during our studio session tomorrow. Here are the details "
"for your reference:\n"
"                </p>\n"
"                <ul style=\"margin:0px 0 16px 0;box-sizing:border-box;\">\n"
"                    <li>\n"
"                        <b>When:<t t-"
"out=\"format_datetime(object.event_id.start, tz=object.mail_tz, "
"dt_format=&quot;long&quot;, lang_code=object.env.lang) or &quot;&quot;"
