"                            Oct 31st - 11:00 AM</t></b>\n"
"                    </li>\n"
"                    <li>\n"
"                        <b>Where:<t t-out=\"object.event_id.location or "
"''\">Frozen Moments Studio</t></b>\n"
"                    </li>\n"
"                </ul>\n"
"                <p style=\"margin:0px 0 16px 0;box-sizing:border-box;"
"\">Please arrive on time to make the\n"
"                    most out\n"
"                    of your session.</p>\n"
"                <p style=\"margin:0px 0 16px 0;box-sizing:border-box;\">More "
"details will follow soon.</p>\n"
"                <p style=\"margin:0px 0 16px 0;box-sizing:border-box;\">If "
"you have any questions or need\n"
"                    to reschedule,\n"
"                    please contact us as soon as possible. </p>\n"
"                <p style=\"margin:0px 0 16px 0;box-sizing:border-box;\">Best "
"regards,</p>\n"
"            \n"
"        "
msgstr ""
"<p style=\"margin:0px 0 16px 0;box-sizing:border-box;\">Bonjour <t t-"
"out=\"object.partner_id.name or '''John Doe'''\"/>,</p>\n"
"                <p style=\"margin:0px 0 16px 0;box-sizing:border-box;\">Nous "
"avons hâte de réaliser\n"
"                    vos photos\n"
"                    lors de notre session en studio prévue demain. Voici les "
