"                    profiter pleinement\n"
"                    de votre session.</p>\n"
"                <p style=\"margin:0px 0 16px 0;box-sizing:border-box;\">Plus "
"d'informations suivront prochainement.</p>\n"
"                <p style=\"margin:0px 0 16px 0;box-sizing:border-box;\">Si "
"vous avez des questions ou devez\n"
"                    reporter le rendez-vous,\n"
"                    veuillez nous contacter le plus rapidement possible.</"
"p>\n"
"                <p style=\"margin:0px 0 16px 0;box-sizing:border-box;"
"\">Cordialement,</p>\n"
"            \n"
"        "

#. module: photography
#: model:mail.template,body_html:photography.order_appointment_booking
msgid ""
"<p style=\"margin:0px 0 16px 0;box-sizing:border-box;\">Hi <t t-"
"out=\"object.partner_id.name or '''John Doe'''\"/>!</p>\n"
"                <p style=\"margin:0px 0 16px 0;box-sizing:border-box;"
"\">You've recently confirmed a Studio\n"
"                    Session with us - we're super glad you chose to work "
"with <t t-out=\"object.company_id.name or '''us'''\">Frozen Moments</t>!</"
"p>\n"
"                <p style=\"margin:0px 0 16px 0;box-sizing:border-box;\">You "
"can book your Studio session\n"
"                    directly via our website by following <a href=\"/book/"
"studio\" style=\"text-decoration:none;box-sizing:border-"
"box;color:#017e84;\">this link</a>\n"
"                </p>\n"
"                <p style=\"margin:0px 0 16px 0;box-sizing:border-box;"
"\">Sessions are 1h30 long, with\n"
"                    usually 20-30min of setup and\n"
"                    45min-1h of proper shooting (with small breaks if "
"needed).</p>\n"
"                <p style=\"margin:0px 0 16px 0;box-sizing:border-box;\">If "
"you have a scheduling issue,\n"
"                    please contact us as soon as\n"
"                    possible and we'll be more than happy to make "
"adaptations!</p>\n"
"                <p style=\"margin:0px 0 16px 0;box-sizing:border-box;\">Kind "
"regards,</p>\n"
"             \n"
"        "
msgstr ""
"<p style=\"margin:0px 0 16px 0;box-sizing:border-box;\">Hello <t t-"
"out=\"object.partner_id.name or '''John Doe'''\"/>!</p>\n"
"                <p style=\"margin:0px 0 16px 0;box-sizing:border-box;\">Vous "
"avez récemment confirmé une séance\n"
"                    en studio avec nous. Nous sommes ravis que vous ayez "
"choisi de travailler avec <t t-out=\"object.company_id.name or "
"'''us'''\">Frozen Moments</t>!</p>\n"
"                <p style=\"margin:0px 0 16px 0;box-sizing:border-box;\">Vous "
"pouvez réserver votre séance en studio\n"
"                    directement sur notre site web via <a href=\"/book/"
"studio\" style=\"text-decoration:none;box-sizing:border-"
"box;color:#017e84;\">ce lien</a>\n"
"                </p>\n"
"                <p style=\"margin:0px 0 16px 0;box-sizing:border-box;\">Les "
"séances durent 1 h 30, avec\n"
"                    généralement 20 - 30 min d'installation et\n"
