#. module: photography
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:photography.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Accounting</strong>: do more than simple invoicing - with Odoo "
"Accounting, you can generate tax reports, manage your invoices and bills and "
"even synchronize payments from your bank account automatically"
msgstr ""
"<strong>Comptabilité</strong> : faites plus que de la simple facturation - "
"avec Odoo Comptabilité, vous pouvez générer des déclarations fiscales, gérer "
"vos factures et même synchroniser automatiquement les paiements depuis votre "
"compte bancaire"

#. module: photography
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:photography.ir_ui_view_1960
msgid ""
"<strong>And more</strong>: Whatever your occasion or preference, I can help "
"you create photos that suit your needs and expectations."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Et plus encore</strong> : Quelle que soit votre occasion ou votre "
"préférence, je vous aide à créer des photos qui répondent à vos besoins et à "
"vos attentes."

#. module: photography
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:photography.ir_ui_view_1959
msgid ""
"<strong>Attract and retain talent</strong> by showcasing your company "
"culture and work environment;"
msgstr ""
"<strong>Attirez et retenez des personnes talentueuses</strong> en mettant en "
"valeur la culture et l'environnement de travail de votre entreprise ;"

#. module: photography
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:photography.ir_ui_view_1960
msgid ""
"<strong>Baby portraits</strong>: Capture the cuteness and innocence of your "
"baby with adorable photos that will make you smile every time you look at "
"them;"
msgstr ""
"<strong>Portraits bébé</strong> : Capturez la tendresse et l'innocence de "
"votre bébé avec d'adorables photos qui vous feront sourire à chaque fois que "
"vous les regarderez ;"

#. module: photography
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:photography.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Email Marketing </strong>and <strong>Social Marketing</strong> "
"<span>: reach out to your clients regarding special events or offers, or "
"prospect for new clients​</span><strong>​</strong>​<strong>​</strong>"
msgstr ""
"<strong>E-mail Marketing </strong>et <strong>Social Marketing</strong> "
"<span>: contactez vos clients au sujet d'événements ou d'offres spéciales, "
"ou prospectez de nouveaux clients​</span><strong>​</strong>​<strong>​</strong>"

#. module: photography
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:photography.ir_ui_view_1959
msgid ""
"<strong>Enhance your reputation and credibility</strong> by documenting your "
"achievements and social responsibility;"
msgstr ""
"<strong>Renforcez votre réputation et votre crédibilité</strong> en "
"documentant vos réussites et votre engagement social ;"

#. module: photography
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:photography.ir_ui_view_1960
msgid ""
"<strong>Family portraits</strong>: Preserve your precious memories and show "
"your family bond with stunning photos that you can cherish for years to come;"
msgstr ""
"<strong>Portraits de famille</strong> : Conservez vos précieux souvenirs et "
"montrez les liens qui unissent votre famille grâce à de superbes photos que "
"vous pourrez chérir pendant des années ;"

#. module: photography
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:photography.ir_ui_view_1959
msgid ""
"<strong>Increase your sales and conversions</strong> by highlighting your "
"products’ features and benefits;"
msgstr ""
"<strong>Augmentez vos ventes et vos conversions</strong> en mettant en avant "
"les caractéristiques et les avantages de vos produits ;"

#. module: photography
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:photography.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Planning</strong>: manage plannings for team members and resources, "
"like a studio room or some hardware"
msgstr ""
"<strong>Planification</strong> : gérez la planification des membres de "
"l'équipe et des ressources, comme une salle de studio ou du matériel "
"informatique"

#. module: photography
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:photography.ir_ui_view_1960
msgid ""
"<strong>Professional portraits</strong>: Impress your clients and employers "
"with polished and confident photos that reflect your personal brand and "
"expertise;"
msgstr ""
"<strong>Portraits professionnels</strong> : Impressionnez vos clients et vos "
"employeurs avec des photos soignées et confiantes qui reflètent l'image de "
"marque et l'expertise de votre entreprise ;"

#. module: photography
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:photography.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Sign</strong>: send contracts to prospects and get the full "
"traceability of their online signature"
msgstr ""
