msgstr "Portraits bébé"

#. module: photography
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:photography.ir_ui_view_1958
msgid ""
"Because your wedding will be one of the most beautiful days of your life. "
"Because you are unique. I want to customize your report as much as possible "
"and give you photos and an album that will make you relive your day full of "
"emotions. During our meetings, you tell me about yourself, your wedding day, "
"what you like and especially what you expect from the photographer who will "
"make your photo report. Then, on my side, I put all my experience as a "
"professional photographer at your service to advise you and make all your "
"wishes come true."
msgstr ""
"Parce que votre mariage sera l’un des plus beaux jours de votre vie. Parce "
"que vous êtes unique. Je souhaite personnaliser votre reportage au maximum "
"et vous offrir des photos ainsi qu’un album qui vous feront revivre cette "
"journée riche en émotions. Lors de nos rendez-vous, vous me parlez de vous, "
"de votre mariage, de ce que vous aimez et surtout de ce que vous attendez du "
"photographe qui accompagnera votre reportage photo. De mon côté, je mets "
"toute mon expérience de photographe professionnel à votre service pour vous "
"conseiller et réaliser tous vos souhaits."

